::Prowl::

Prowl looks at Plintissa, a bit confused. "Um, sure. I'd go apologise to 
Ramhorn if I were you," he says, "He seemed pretty pissed."

He looks down at Iron Raptor, asleep in his arms. An exciting feeling goes 
through him as he looks at her peaceful (to him at least) face. He stands 
there for a few seconds, looking at her.

Prowl blinks. What was he doing? Staring at her when he should get her to her 
quarters.

He chuckles, walking off towards her quarters.
